# HSM collector conformance v1 — bar period rollover contract (the only wall-clock fixture).
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|...
# Actions:
# sleep_ms|milliseconds
# expect_all_bars_aligned|period_ms
# expect_bar_open_times_increasing
# expect_bar_count_total|expected
# expect_sent_count_between|min|max|timeout_seconds
# Contract notes:
# - A bar rolls when a value arrives after the current bar's CloseTime: the closed bar is
#   published and a fresh aligned bar opens. Idle periods publish nothing (no empty bars).
# - Only the first case asserts an exact value distribution; the rest use timing-immune
#   invariants (count total, alignment, monotone open times) to stay flake-free.

bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|create_collector
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|create_int_bar_sensor|contract/roll/strict|2000|0
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|start
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|add_bar_int|0|1
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|add_bar_int|0|2
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|add_bar_int|0|3
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|sleep_ms|2600
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|add_bar_int|0|10
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|stop
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_sent_count|2
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_bar_field|0|count|3
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_bar_field|0|min|1
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_bar_field|0|max|3
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_bar_field|1|count|1
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_bar_field|1|last|10
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_all_bars_aligned|2000
bar_rolls_on_add_after_close_strict|expect_bar_open_times_increasing

bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|create_collector
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|create_int_bar_sensor|contract/roll/invariant|500|0
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|start
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|add_bar_int|0|1
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|add_bar_int|0|2
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|sleep_ms|700
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|add_bar_int|0|9
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|add_bar_int|0|10
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|stop
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|expect_sent_count_between|2|4|10
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|expect_bar_count_total|4
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|expect_all_bars_aligned|500
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|expect_bar_open_times_increasing
bar_rollover_no_value_lost_invariants|expect_bar_field|-1|last|10

bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|create_collector
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|create_int_bar_sensor|contract/roll/gap|500|0
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|start
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|add_bar_int|0|1
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|sleep_ms|1200
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|add_bar_int|0|2
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|stop
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|expect_sent_count|2
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|expect_bar_count_total|2
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|expect_all_bars_aligned|500
bar_rollover_gap_produces_no_empty_bars|expect_bar_open_times_increasing
